{"tid":895076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怒爆中國航空展客機無恥抄襲 原設計者嘆：提告絕對沒用","createTime":"2018-11-09T01:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T04:33:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e95611bee9b926c4e471fa8a795cdd84e9248654","tid":895076,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpmUeqVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpmUeqVc.jpg&h=35375609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中國珠海航空展CR929客機被爆抄襲，原設計公司總工程師兼總經理大嘆，對中國提告沒有用。（美聯社）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國現正舉辦珠海航空展，但有俄國媒體爆料，展出中的CR929客機是抄襲自俄國設計公司的作品，原設計者也在受訪時怒批中方「無恥抄襲」，卻也坦言控告中國侵權是「絕對沒有用的」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，宣稱「中俄合資」的CR929客機在珠海航空展亮相，同步在聯合航空製造公司（ОАК）網站上介紹性能，但俄羅斯設計公司「Atom」總工程師兼總經理庫鋅恩（Maxim Kuzin）控訴，CR929客機是該公司在2015年投標上海客機標案的作品，事隔3年竟被對方瓢竊，還找上俄國聯航合作。<br />\n<br />\n庫鋅恩受訪時難掩激動情緒，他指出，「不知道怎麼才能文明地表達自己的態度」，但中國沒品的瓢竊手段的確令自己相當訝異，但公司不打算對中方提告，此事能清楚了解當局的態度，因此任何法律行動都是「絕對沒有用的」；外媒則提到，在中國設計侵權官司成立難度極高，只要抄襲者將部分內容稍做修改，都可稱為創新作品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2606766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2606766&d=Oghd3ciEbQH%2B5GyYlYTWV1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=9077aeda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2606766&h=2d6ae415\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2606766</a>"},{"pid":"97c132db3a18fe48e8dea88d738aed8e295b8cd1","tid":895076,"uid":45830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"飛一架，射一架，佢夠西膽出聲。"},{"pid":"78df853d320500f8bbdd49ceee7d37923e041852","tid":895076,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3464e49431178a32bfbf499c6e3f0842f3975d","tid":895076,"uid":98289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:15:53.000Z","msg":"俄佬仲唔發火咪繼續俾契弟偷偷摸摸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd712ad5a73eeb5409a4c6e0fe2473e57a8af8f3","tid":895076,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}